{"name": "odoo12-addon-mail-activity-team", "metadata": {"name": "odoo12-addon-mail-activity-team", "version": "12.0.1.2.3", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Framework :: Odoo", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/social", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo12-addon-mail-activity-board", "odoo"], "summary": "Add Teams to Activities", "upload_time": 1623929726}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fsocial-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/social\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/social/tree/12.0/mail_activity_team\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/social-12-0/social-12-0-mail_activity_team\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runbot-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runbot\n    :target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/205/12.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Mail Activity Team\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module adds the possibility to assign teams to activities.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo set up new teams:\n\n1. Go to *Settings / Activate developer mode*\n2. Go to *Settings / Technical / Email / Activity Teams*\n3. Create a new Team and assign (optionally) the models in which it will\n   be used, and the members of the team.\n\nYou can also assign a user to Activity teams going to\n*Settings / Users & Companies / Users*, and in the *Preferences* tab, field\nActivity Teams.\n\nWhen you create a new activity the application will propose the user's\nassigned team.\n\nYou can report on the activities assigned to a team going to\n*Dashboards / Activities*, and then filter by a specific team or group by\nteams.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/social/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/social/issues/new?body=module:%20mail_activity_team%0Aversion:%2012.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Eficent\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Eficent](https://www.eficent.com):\n\n  - Jordi Ballester Alomar (<mailto:jordi.ballester@eficent.com>)\n  - Miquel Ra\u00efch (<mailto:miquel.raich@eficent.com>)\n\n- Enric Tobella \\<<mailto:etobella@creublanca.es>>\n\n- [Tecnativa](https://www.tecnativa.com):\n\n  - David Vidal\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/social](https://github.com/OCA/social/tree/12.0/mail_activity_team) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_team.models.mail_activity_mixin", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 Eficent Business and IT Consulting Services, S.L.", "Copyright 2021 Tecnativa - David Vidal", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_team.models.mail_activity_mixin.MailActivityMixin", "bases": ["models.AbstractModel"], "methods": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_team.models.mail_activity_mixin.MailActivityMixin._compute_activity_team_user_ids", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_team.models.mail_activity_mixin.MailActivityMixin._search_activity_team_user_ids", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "operator", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "operand", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mail_activity_team.models.mail_activity_mixin.MailActivityMixin.activity_schedule", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "act_type_xmlid", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "date_deadline", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "summary", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "note", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "**act_values", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["With automatic activities, the user onchange won't act so we must\nensure the right group is set and no exceptions are raised due to\nuser-team missmatch. We can hook onto `act_values` dict as it's passed\nto the create activity method."]}], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.m